## Context

The Express/TypeScript API has posts and comments CRUD routes but no authentication. Write operations are open to anyone. The `jsonwebtoken` package is already installed. A comprehensive test suite (`tests/auth.test.ts`) defines the exact expected behavior. This plan wires up JWT-based register/login endpoints, an auth middleware, and ownership enforcement on all write routes.

